BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Meditate with a Monk
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county/
UID:event_313714623@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260326T184133Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260329T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260329T100000
SUMMARY:Join us for Guided Buddhist Meditation and time for questions
DESCRIPTION:Meditate with a Monk in Sonoma County\nNew and experienced med
 itators are welcome. We will start with direct guidance to begin the pract
 ice and allow time to experience the silence of meditation on your own. Th
 ere will be time at the end for your questions regarding meditation practi
 ce.\n\nYou may stay on for a potluck meal at 11:00 am. Welcome to bring a 
 dish to share.\n\nThis is followed by Sutta Study program from 1:00 to 2:3
 0 pm.\n\nWe meet outdoors in the Dhammadharini Monastery Garden in the Sal
 a Pavillion\, as long as conducive weather lasts.\n\nCome in person\, or r
 egister at [here](https://www.dhammadharini.net/event-details/sunday-morni
 ng-guided-meditation-questions-2) to attend online
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county
 /events/313714623/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260309T170556Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260309T170556Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Meditate with a Monk
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county/
UID:event_313714737@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260326T184133Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260329T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260329T100000
SUMMARY:Mindfulness Sunday Meditation: Cultivating Consciousness
DESCRIPTION:Meditate with a Monk in Sonoma County\nJoin us for a transform
 ative workshop on mindfulness meditation and cultivating consciousness. Di
 ve deep into the teachings of Theravada Buddhism\, focusing on insight med
 itation to develop a clear understanding of the nature of the mind and con
 sciousness. This workshop will include guided meditation sessions to help 
 you strengthen your meditation practice and cultivate mindfulness in your 
 daily life. Whether you are a beginner or an experienced meditator\, this 
 workshop offers a welcoming space to explore the depths of your own consci
 ousness and enhance your spiritual journey. Come together with like-minded
  individuals to deepen your practice and connect with the wisdom of Therav
 ada Buddhism\, and provide an opportunity to deepen mindfulness\, wisdom\,
  and inner stillness.\nOur sessions are led by Bhikkhunis closely associat
 ed with our Dhammadharini Sangha. Check out the [recording from the past e
 vent](https://youtube.com/live/s07U2kzWoWk?feature=share) on our YouTube c
 hannel.\nYou’re also welcome to join us in person at Dhammadharini Monas
 tery\, in the peaceful setting of our outdoor Dana Sala Pavilion\nRegister
  for this event on Dhammadharini's website to receive the address:\n[https
 ://www.dhammadharini.net/event-details/sunday-morning-guided-meditation-qu
 estions-2](https://www.dhammadharini.net/event-details/sunday-morning-guid
 ed-meditation-questions-2)\nCheck out the sangha website at\n[https://www.
 dhammadharini.net](https://www.dhammadharini.net/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county
 /events/313714737/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260309T170813Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260309T170813Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Meditate with a Monk
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county/
UID:event_313544474@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260326T184133Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260329T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260329T143000
SUMMARY:Read and discuss the teachings of the Buddha
DESCRIPTION:Meditate with a Monk in Sonoma County\nWe study the early Budd
 hist texts by reading aloud and discussing. The reading will be announced 
 each week\n\n1:00pm. Meditation\n1:15-2:30pm. Sutta reading and discussion
 \n\nYou may come early for a potluck meal at 11:00 am. Welcome to bring a 
 dish to share.\n\nWe meet outdoors in the Dhammadharini Monastery's Garden
  in the Sala Pavillion\, as long as conducive weather lasts.\n\nCome in pe
 rson\, or register at [here](https://www.dhammadharini.net/event-details/s
 unday-morning-guided-meditation-questions-2) to attend online
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county
 /events/313544474/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260226T200516Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260226T200516Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
